{"tid":685445,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解中醫鳩吹都解釋到腎虛會甩頭髮","createTime":"2018-05-31T11:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T12:11:26.000Z","uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"11d4622e4f1e5d5de570ca2e18e6a0d648786a78","tid":685445,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:53:24.000Z","msg":"中醫:<br />\n中醫認為「腎藏精，其華在髮」，腎精可化生氣血，通過督脈為頭髮加注營養，從而變得健康濃密、烏黑及有光澤。腎虛的人同時會有氣血不足問題，令頭髮、毛囊得不到氣血濡養，導致頭髮變白、稀少枯萎、無光澤，甚至受脫髮困擾。<br />\n<br />\n西醫:<br />\nErythropoietin promotes hair shaft growth in cultured human hair follicles and modulates hair growth in mice.<br />\nKang BM, et al. J Dermatol Sci. 2010.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/20554434/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fm%2Fpubmed%2F20554434%2F&d=Ak3NfAWZMzwFovJ%2BXfxSZOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=42c6fb00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/m/pubmed/20554434/</a><br />\n<br />\nHuman hair follicles are an extrarenal source and a nonhematopoietic target of erythropoietin<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fasebj.org/doi/abs/10.1096/fj.07-8628com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fasebj.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1096%2Ffj.07-8628com&d=Ak3NfAWZMzwFovJ%2BXfxSZOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=312e7f32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fasebj.org/doi/abs/10.1096/fj.07-8628com</a><br />\n<br />\n明明中醫都冇erythroprotein呢樣野"},{"pid":"14b1838525d0be93f95108012e8e65b938fa7451","tid":685445,"uid":149487,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"因為唔係鳩吹"},{"pid":"275b2f2d21d32bb9588be6c3e38f2c223a67311f","tid":685445,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:58:37.000Z","msg":"中醫<strong>可能</strong>係比較先進既技術<br />\n現今科技仲未解釋到姐"},{"pid":"550f4343650d5bdba5768cbe38050cbe4cc30a89","tid":685445,"uid":54923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"做左咁多人體實驗的出黎既結果"},{"pid":"91e86b2b9bf2da48a31b6859dab7314fbd4ebe13","tid":685445,"uid":138502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<strong>肝腎不足</strong><br />\n<br />\n腎主骨，藏精，其華在髮。肝藏血，髮為血之餘，肝腎精血同源，血乃精所化，精血充足則毛髮光澤。肝腎不足，則頭髮失去生長之源，不能濡養而脫落。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>脾胃濕熱</strong><br />\n<br />\n脾主運化，為後天之本，脾氣虛弱，或過食肥甘厚味、辛辣、酒類，以致脾胃失常，水濕內聚化熱，濕熱上蒸，引起頭髮黏膩而脫落。<br />\n<br />\n無論是肝腎不足或是脾胃濕熱，皆可有先天和後天的因素，即是天生肝腎欠佳，或是天生脾胃較虛，所以若先天差，再加上後天飲食不節，脫髮問題便更嚴重。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://wp.3phk.com/cp-3-15052017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwp.3phk.com%2Fcp-3-15052017%2F&d=Ak3NfAWZMzwFovJ%2BXfxSZOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=c948deb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://wp.3phk.com/cp-3-15052017/</a><br />\n肝腎脾胃 四個梗有一個中掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d839e65b4bca72b414325a538509bb5c7896e7","tid":685445,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"問下英國佬同德國佬點睇"},{"pid":"fd5b302a4b79a27c527859d182e314bba91a6c2e","tid":685445,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"statistic"}]}